<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n37009h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n37" href="#n37009h">N37 (VI.B.28A)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n37all.htm#n37009h"> 9(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 201 a live pickpocket</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[<font size="-1">SUNDRIES AND AN AUTOBIOGRAPHY</font>]</font>: Barnum issued handbills announcing that for the last day of the fair the management had obtained an unusual attraction, &ldquo;<mark>a live pickpocket</mark>&rdquo;, who would be exhibited, safely handcuffed, without extra charge. Some farmers brought their children ten miles to see the extraordinary sight. <small> M.R. Werner, <a name="MRWP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#MRWP"><cite title="source">P.T. Barnum</cite></a> (1923) 201</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
